{"tid":1249680,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"求文宣同 6 月12 喺金鐘特別係中信嘅人入嚟幫下手","createTime":"2019-06-21T19:16:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T05:39:11.000Z","uid":267059,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9c089cdd39dd97736e079145f43730780a15c776","tid":1249680,"uid":267059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T19:16:00.000Z","msg":"如果想要國際關注同用外媒打輿論戰 <br />\n<br />\n唔該巴絲去 Twitter <br />\n好多外媒記者都用 Twitter <br />\n<br />\n收到 dm, Ny times 想寫 6 月12 單嘢 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qPFNk18.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqPFNk18.png&h=4bcc9aa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇過佢啲 followers <br />\n呢個堅係佢哋記者嚟 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FJz2Und.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFJz2Und.png&h=37ccd53f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我會覆不過都想有熟記者嗰行嘅人提點下<br />\n<br />\n同埋有冇人有第一手料當日在場可以分享事發經過 <br />\n<br />\n---<br />\n<br />\n另外想講, 雖然現行抗爭方式係好過長佔, 不過對我哋嚟講長遠會消耗民意, 希望文宣同輿論打得好啲, 唔好畀差佬老屈。<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油"},{"pid":"e58e8e2a4b663257a043b86910e7b2a23e80f040","tid":1249680,"uid":267059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T19:22:45.000Z","msg":"仲有你哋玩 Twitter 好心 up 返個頭像啦 <br />\n<br />\n外媒會覺得你哋係 Bot 唔會 Approach 你 <br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RnRwNP6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRnRwNP6.png&h=ac89ca64&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"49f0cdcaf11a89b06a6c2fd7f96e5452059c6093","tid":1249680,"uid":267059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T20:16:46.000Z","msg":"push <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ce36cee82b45f851d8dea9161fbbbbe612cf3b1","tid":1249680,"uid":63511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T20:55:11.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"5637048ae3a81754f06632d490c454a9a7115980","tid":1249680,"uid":267059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT